---
// index.astro - Profile/About page (Homepage)
// Bio content only - profile sidebar is in BaseLayout

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="ChiWei Hu (William) | Portfolio">
  <section class="bio-content">
    <h2 class="bio__heading">About</h2>

    <p>
      I'm a Master's student in Computer Science at the
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.usc.edu/">University of Southern California (USC)</a>,
      with background in biochemistry and systems engineering.
    </p>

    <p>
      Previously, I worked as a Software Engineer Intern at
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://about.meta.com/">Meta</a> and as a Software Engineer at
      <span class="bio__keyword">Strong Electro-Mechanical</span>,
      gaining experience across both large-scale tech and industrial systems.
      I received my Master's degree in Biochemistry from
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.ntu.edu.tw/">National Taiwan University</a> and my Bachelor's degree in Life Science from
      <a class="bio__link" href="https://www.ncku.edu.tw/">National Cheng Kung University</a>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="bio__heading">Experience</h2>

    <p>
      I have over two years of experience in software engineering, with a focus on <span class="bio__keyword">backend systems</span>, system integration, and performance-critical applications. My technical work spans <span class="bio__keyword">C++</span>, <span class="bio__keyword">C#</span>, <span class="bio__keyword">Python</span>, and <span class="bio__keyword">Rust</span>, along with experience in <span class="bio__keyword">databases</span> and <span class="bio__keyword">distributed systems</span>.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Meta, I built a Rust-based <span class="bio__keyword">CLI debugging tool</span> on top of <span class="bio__keyword">Apache Thrift</span> to crawl and analyze records from interal storage, improving issue triaging efficiency. I also implemented <span class="bio__keyword">webhook replay</span> functionality in the "WhatsApp Business" platform to ensure reliable cross-system message delivery.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Strong, I developed automation systems for semiconductor manufacturing equipment, improving process efficiency and system reliability through <span class="bio__keyword">SECS</span>-based communication and real-time monitoring systems.
    </p>

    <p>
      Beyond industry experience, I have built low-level systems such as an <a class="bio__link" href="/projects#weenix">operating system kernel</a> and developed <a class="bio__link" href="/projects#multimedia">multimedia processing pipelines</a>, demonstrating strong fundamentals in systems programming and performance optimization.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
